com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util
Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util.Preferences

public final class Preferences
extends Object

This preferences class contains all settings that are required in the extension. It serves as a facade abstracting Moneydance's UserPreferences (received from the FeatureModuleContext) and the configuration values that are read from a configuration file.
